announcement to make.

1513
01:47:49,376 --> 01:47:51,580
Next week,
I have an auction in London.

1514
01:47:51,918 --> 01:47:55,283
It will be the finest of my career
and the very last.

1515
01:47:58,209 --> 01:47:59,868
(indistinct chatter)

1516
01:48:01,001 --> 01:48:03,833
They say he's been seen
recently in female company.

1517
01:48:04,001 --> 01:48:05,743
- Who? Virgil?
- Yes.

1518
01:48:05,918 --> 01:48:10,042
It's finally come home to him that the
worst sexual perversion is chastity.

1519
01:48:11,251 --> 01:48:13,870
