I got dizzy in the car yesterday.

1528
01:48:36,918 --> 01:48:40,449
Don't let it get to you. We have
all the time in the world to travel.

1529
01:48:40,626 --> 01:48:42,782
- We're ready, Mr. Oldman.
- I'm coming.

1530
01:48:43,668 --> 01:48:45,872
Have you heard
from our young friends?

1531
01:48:46,043 --> 01:48:48,827
Constantly.
I'm never left on my own.

1532
01:48:49,001 --> 01:48:51,039
Good. Give them my love.

1533
01:48:52,209 --> 01:48:54,876
- I can hear you've got to go.
- Yes.

1534
01:48:55,959 --> 01:48:59,491
- But I can't wait to get back home.
- Good luck, my darling.

