1538
01:49:13,084 --> 01:49:14,625
Any advance?

1539
01:49:17,626 --> 01:49:20,115
£12,500,000 on the telephone.

1540
01:49:21,626 --> 01:49:23,617
Any more?

1541
01:49:23,793 --> 01:49:26,411
All done at £12,500,000.

1542
01:49:26,751 --> 01:49:30,247
