I've sent you one of my paintings.

1554
01:50:18,834 --> 01:50:20,624
I promise I won't burn it.

1555
01:50:30,918 --> 01:50:32,458
Claire.

1556
01:50:34,001 --> 01:50:35,542
Claire, I'm back!

1557
01:50:37,543 --> 01:50:39,083
Hello?

1558
01:50:42,293 --> 01:50:45,160
- Have you seen Miss Claire?
- (housekeeper) No, sir.

1559
